# --- Project-specific files ---
# Usually, you keep .project and .classpath if you want others to 
# import the project directly into Eclipse, but many developers 
# prefer to ignore them and rely on Maven/Gradle to regenerate them.
#.project
#.classpath

# --- Build Folders ---
# Compiled class files
*.class

# Log files
*.log

